<L>__{interior bathroom on uncle louis (sort of)}
<A>__{it's a huge old fashioned bathroom. the centerpiece is a deep ancient bathtub on faded gild feet. there's a rippling shadow of a body under the bath water. johana gasps.}
<C>__{jacques}
<D>__{don't be afraid. it's my uncle... louis.}
<A>__{he goes to the tub and pinches the end of a tube. uncle louis, underwater, has been breathing through it. louis' head pops out of the water, furious.}
<C>__{uncle louis}
<D>__{assassin!}
